Text: Can you post the screencaps in the comments?

Why even upload a movie with missing parts ? I hate to bash uploaders but  the "noob" title from the leaker was transferred to you  when you uploaded it. This community is so stagnant with shitty quality uploads and it baffles me why it is perpetuated. 
In all seriousness thank you for the upload and your time working on it.I do not think it is too much to ask, please for the love of god, to try a little quality control if you feel so strongly about the copy and the leaker !
